description:
WebMarkupMin.WebForms contains 3 Web Forms page classes: CompressedPage (only supports GZIP/Deflate compression), MinifiedAndCompressedHtmlPage (supports HTML minification and GZIP/Deflate compression) and MinifiedAndCompressedXhtmlPage (supports XHTML minification and GZIP/Deflate compression); and 3 master page classes: CompressedMasterPage (only supports GZIP/Deflate compression), MinifiedAndCompressedHtmlMasterPage (supports HTML minification and GZIP/Deflate compression) and MinifiedAndCompressedXhtmlMasterPage (supports XHTML minification and GZIP/Deflate compression).

–°lasses of the Web Forms pages and master pages cannot be used together.
releaseNotes: Now during the minification of markup is checked excess of the maximum response size.

title: Web Markup Minifier: ASP.NET Web Forms Extensions
